# KiCad Minimalist Gitignore
# Only the primary design files will be tracked in Git.
# Everything else is ignored.

# Ignore everything by default
*

# Allow the .gitignore file itself
!/.gitignore

# Allow the 3 mandatory KiCad design files
!*.kicad_pro
!*.kicad_sch
!*.kicad_pcb

# Optional: Allow project-specific symbol and footprint libraries if they exist
!*.kicad_sym
!*.kicad_fp

# Ignore all directories (like backups or fabrication) unless they contain one of the allowed files above
!*/
